description: Log intrinsic growth rate of COTS (year^-1)
enhanced_semantic_description: Crown of Thorns starfish population intrinsic growth potential

description: Log carrying capacity for COTS (indiv/m2)
enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum sustainable Crown of Thorns starfish population density

description: Log COTS predation rate on coral (m2/indiv/year)
enhanced_semantic_description: Crown of Thorns starfish coral consumption and predation intensity

description: Log half-saturation constant for COTS predation (indiv/m2)
enhanced_semantic_description: COTS density at which predation rate on coral is half its maximum (captures interference/satiation at high COTS densities)

description: Log selectivity for fast coral (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Selective predation preference for fast-growing coral species

description: Log selectivity for slow coral (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Selective predation preference for slow-growing coral species

description: Log intrinsic growth rate of fast coral (year^-1)
enhanced_semantic_description: Fast-growing coral species population regeneration and recovery rate

description: Log intrinsic growth rate of slow coral (year^-1)
enhanced_semantic_description: Slow-growing coral species population regeneration and recovery rate

description: Log carrying capacity for fast coral (%)
enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum sustainable coverage for fast-growing coral species

description: Log carrying capacity for slow coral (%)
enhanced_semantic_description: Maximum sustainable coverage for slow-growing coral species

description: Log environmental effect scaling (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Environmental forcing scale for Crown of Thorns starfish dynamics

description: Log SD for COTS observation error (lognormal)
enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty and variability in Crown of Thorns abundance

description: Log SD for fast coral observation error (lognormal)
enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty for fast-growing coral species coverage

description: Log SD for slow coral observation error (lognormal)
enhanced_semantic_description: Measurement uncertainty for slow-growing coral species coverage

description: Logit probability of outbreak trigger (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Probabilistic threshold for Crown of Thorns starfish population outbreak

description: Log mean duration of outbreak (years)
enhanced_semantic_description: Characteristic duration and persistence of starfish population explosion

description: Log small constant for numerical stability
enhanced_semantic_description: Numerical stabilization constant for computational model convergence

description: Log half-saturation constant for coral limitation on COTS growth (same units as coral_avail)
enhanced_semantic_description: Half-saturation constant for effect of coral availability on COTS population growth; controls how strongly COTS growth is limited when coral is scarce
citations: Pratchett, M.S. et al. (2014) Limits to crown-of-thorns starfish outbreaks: coral depletion and recruitment limitation. Marine Biology.

description: Hill coefficient for COTS predation functional response (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Controls the steepness of the nonlinear (Hill-type) increase in COTS predation efficiency as COTS density rises; higher values produce more threshold-like, outbreak-driven coral mortality

description: Hill coefficient for coral limitation on COTS growth (unitless)
enhanced_semantic_description: Controls the steepness of the nonlinear (Hill-type) effect of coral availability on COTS population growth; higher values produce a sharper threshold for outbreak onset as coral cover increases.
citations: Pratchett, M.S. et al. (2014) Limits to crown-of-thorns starfish outbreaks: coral depletion and recruitment limitation. Marine Biology.

description: Log Allee constant for fast coral recovery (same units as fast coral cover)
enhanced_semantic_description: Minimum fast coral cover required for effective population recovery; models recruitment limitation and slow recovery at low cover (Allee effect)
citations: Mumby, P.J. et al. (2007) Thresholds and the resilience of Caribbean coral reefs. Nature.

description: Log Allee constant for slow coral recovery (same units as slow coral cover)
enhanced_semantic_description: Minimum slow coral cover required for effective population recovery; models recruitment limitation and slow recovery at low cover (Allee effect)
citations: Mumby, P.J. et al. (2007) Thresholds and the resilience of Caribbean coral reefs. Nature.
